		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://cml.ics.uci.edu/2016/11/phd-research-fellowships/" title="Permalink to PhD Research Fellowships" rel="bookmark">PhD Research Fellowships</a></h1>				<span class="entry-format genericon">Standard</span>			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>The Computer Science department at UC Irvine is seeking applicants for PhD research fellowships in artificial intelligence, machine learning, and their related applications, including topics such as deep learning, statistical learning, graphical models, information extraction, computer vision, high-dimensional data analysis, and more.</p>
<p>Please see <a href="http://cml.ics.uci.edu//wp-content/uploads/cml/PhD-Research-Fellowships-2016.pdf">this flier</a> for more information.</p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
