		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://cml.ics.uci.edu/2015/02/alexander-ihler-gives-short-course-on-approximate-inference-at-mlss/" title="Permalink to Ihler gives short course on approximate inference at MLSS" rel="bookmark">Ihler gives short course on approximate inference at MLSS</a></h1>				<span class="entry-format genericon">Standard</span>			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Center Director Alexander Ihler gave a half-day course on approximate inference in graphical models as part of the <a href="http://rp-www.cs.usyd.edu.au/~mlss/#home">2015 Machine Learning Summer School</a> in Sydney Australia.  <a href="http://mlss.cc/">MLSS</a> is a long-running series of summer schools around the world for graduate students and researchers who want to apply machine learning methods to their research problems.  His lecture is available online <a href="https://youtu.be/p50Fbv-3qaM">here</a>.</p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
